text: Aerenea albilarvata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1866. It is known from French Guiana, Brazil and Peru.BioLib.cz - Aerenea albilarvata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1866
